bjects like "},{"code":"OUDSSelect","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSelectComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSelectComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference"},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SelectComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"select"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Select","type":"text"}]},{"text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":"),","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":") and spaces (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":").","type"